# rxx_pi8 — e^{i(π/8)X⊗X} = (H⊗H)·rzz_pi8·(H⊗H) (해밀토니안 시뮬 XX 상호작용). X=HZH 기저변환. plan=봉인 h_gate·rzz_pi8, no MatrixGate. golden=closed-form Pauli 지수.
```json id=app_meta
{"id": "rxx_pi8", "n_sys": 2, "n_anc": 0}
