```python id=app_golden
import numpy as np
X = np.array([[0,1],[1,0]],complex); XX = np.kron(X, X)
golden = (np.cos(np.pi/8)*np.eye(4) + 1j*np.sin(np.pi/8)*XX).astype(complex)
```
